<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7629474>
    dc:description "Fig. 56. Georeferenced collection records of Lasioglossum (D.) puteulanum Gibbs, 2009 (black squares) and predicted distribution by maximum entropy ecological niche modelling in Maxent (colour shading). Warmer colours indicate higher cloglog probability of occurrence. Because many coastal records lacked soil data, the model was generated without soil type as an environmental variable." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7629474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7629550>
    dc:description "Fig. 92. T1 anterior slope. A. Lasioglossum puteulanum Gibbs, 2009, ♀, coriarious. B. L. angelicum sp. nov., ♀, smooth and shiny. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7629550/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7629568>
    dc:description "Fig. 101. Face. A. Lasioglossum puteulanum Gibbs, 2009, ♀, slightly longer. B. L. tegulare (Robertson, 1890), ♀, slightly shorter. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7629568/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7629608>
    dc:description "Fig. 118. Face. A. Lasioglossum puteulanum Gibbs, 2009, ♂, slightly longer. B. L. tegulare (Robertson, 1890), ♂, slightly shorter. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7629608/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

